<center><%= image_tag "yointro-logo.png" %></center><br><br>

<div class="container">
<div class="row-fluid">
<div class="span8">

<h3>What is Yo'intro</h3>
A service that allows you to quickly send an email introducing 2 people. 
<h3>How is it different from writing a regular email?</h3>
Yo'intro will automatically pre-fill the entire email for you. All you have to do is choose your recipients and hit send!
<h3>What if I have more questions?</h3>
We will soon have a complete FAQ section, but until then please email us at <%= mail_to "yointroapp@gmail.com", "yointroapp@gmail.com" %>
</div>

<div class="span4">
<h2>Sign up</h2>
<div class="sign-up">

<%= form_for(resource, :as => resource_name, :url => registration_path(resource_name)) do |f| %>
  <%= devise_error_messages! %>

  <div>
  <%= f.email_field :email, :class=> "input_field", :autofocus => true, :placeholder => "Email" %></div>
<br>
  <div>
  <%= f.password_field :password, :class=> "input_field", :placeholder => "Password" %></div>
<br>
  <div>
  <%= f.password_field :password_confirmation, :class=> "input_field", :placeholder => "Confirm Password" %></div>

  <div><%= f.submit "Sign up" %></div>
<% end %>

<%= render "devise/shared/links" %>
</div>
</div>
</div>
